<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Wandering Brazil</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@500&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Wandering Brazil</h1>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="overlay"></div>
  <div class="content">
    <h2>Discover Brazil<br>through local eyes</h2>
    <p>
      Exclusive, tailor-made travel itineraries designed by a Brazilian expert.
      No templates. No generic routes. Just your journey.
    </p>

    <div class="buttons">
      <a href="#" class="btn primary">Start Your Journey</a>
      <a href="#" class="btn secondary">Chat on WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="image-break lencois"></section>

<section class="how">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>How it works</h2>

    <div class="grid">
      <div>
        <h3>1. Share your vision</h3>
        <p>Tell us how you like to travel, what excites you and what you expect.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3>2. We curate your experience</h3>
        <p>Your itinerary is crafted from scratch, based entirely on your profile.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3>3. Travel with confidence</h3>
        <p>Experience Brazil with clarity, safety and local insight.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="why">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Why Wandering Brazil</h2>

    <div class="grid">
      <div>
        <h3>Brazilian perspective</h3>
        <p>Real knowledge from someone who lives the culture — not from the outside.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3>True personalization</h3>
        <p>Every journey is unique. No pre-made packages, ever.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3>Limited clients</h3>
        <p>We work with a select number of travelers to ensure quality and attention.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="image-grid">
  <div class="img rio"></div>
  <div class="img sp"></div>
</section>

<section class="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Your insider in Brazil</h2>
    <p>
      Brazil is more than a destination — it’s a complex, vibrant and deeply unique country.
      <br><br>
      With Wandering Brazil, you don’t just visit. You experience it through local knowledge,
      thoughtful curation and a journey designed exclusively for you.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Start planning your journey</h2>
    <p>Choose how you'd like to begin</p>

    <div class="buttons vertical">
      <a href="LINK_DO_FORMULARIO_AQUI" class="btn primary">Fill out the travel form</a>
      <a href="#" class="btn secondary">Chat on WhatsApp</a>
      <a href="#" class="btn secondary">Telegram</a>
      <a href="#" class="btn primary">Book a Zoom Call</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2026 Wandering Brazil</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>

/* HERO IMAGE (IPANEMA SUNSET) */
.hero {
  height: 90vh;
  background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507525428034-b723cf961d3e') center/cover no-repeat;
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  text-align: center;
  color: white;
}

/* LENÇÓIS */
.image-break {
  height: 60vh;
}

.lencois {
  background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1501785888041-af3ef285b470') center/cover no-repeat;
}

/* GRID IMAGES */
.image-grid {
  display: flex;
}

.image-grid .img {
  width: 50%;
  height: 400px;
}

/* RIO (CRISTO) */
.rio {
  background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494475673543-6a6a27143b04') center/cover no-repeat;
}

/* SÃO PAULO */
.sp {
  background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505761671935-60b3a7427bad') center/cover no-repeat;
}
